Natalia Brassova and Grand Duke Michael have been dating since 15th Oct 1911.

About

Russian Royal Natalia Brassova was born Natalia Sergeyevna Sheremetyevskaya on 27th June, 1880 in Moscow ?, Empire of Russia and passed away on 26th Jan 1952 Laennec charity hospital, Paris, French Fourth Republic aged 71. She is most remembered for Mistress and latter wife of Grand Duke Mikhail Alexandrovich of Russia. Her zodiac sign is Cancer.
